    <item>
      <title>逃离餐厅通货膨胀率高达 90% 的土耳其食客纷纷涌向希腊</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/turkish-diners-fleeing-90-restaurant-inflation-flock-to-greece</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在旅游旺季，土耳其一些度假城市的餐馆都空了一半，因为许多当地人发现到邻国希腊度假比在自己国家举世闻名的度假胜地住宿和吃饭更便宜。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/turkish-diners-fleeing-90-restaurant-inflation-flock-to-greece</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 07:30:01 GMT</pubDate>
